---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="Our affiliate relationships and how they work.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold font-heading text-foreground mb-6">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-foreground-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Selcurate is a participant in affiliate programs including Amazon Associates,
        ShareASale, CJ Affiliate, and direct brand partner programs. This means when
        you click certain links on this site and make a purchase, we may earn a
        commission at no additional cost to you.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our content is based on aggregated user reviews, manufacturer specifications,
        and community feedback — not personal product testing. We clearly label all
        affiliate links and display this disclosure at the top of every article that
        contains affiliate links.
      </p>

      <p>
        We are NOT paid to write positive content about any product. Commission rates
        do not influence our content or product presentation order. Products are
        organized by aggregated user ratings and objective specifications.
      </p>

      <h2>How Affiliate Links Work</h2>
      <p>
        When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, the retailer pays us a
        small commission. The price you pay is exactly the same whether you use our
        link or go directly to the retailer's website. These commissions help us
        maintain this site and continue producing research-backed content.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Programs We Participate In</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — Products across all categories</li>
        <li><strong>ShareASale</strong> — FlexiSpot, Keychron, and other brands</li>
        <li><strong>CJ Affiliate</strong> — Logitech, Grammarly, and other brands</li>
        <li><strong>Direct partnerships</strong> — Autonomous, Secretlab, Branch, NordVPN, 1Password, and others</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about our affiliate relationships, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@selcurate.com">hello@selcurate.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
